1. Sibling project: aozora (Apache-2.0 OR MIT)
================================================================================

aozora-obsidian invokes the `aozora` parser to translate Aozora Bunko
notation into HTML inside the editor's preview pane. The integration shape
— bundled WASM vs spawned binary — is recorded in ADR-0001. aozora is
dual-licensed under Apache-2.0 OR MIT; see
https://github.com/P4suta/aozora/blob/main/NOTICE for the third-party
attributions.


